@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oyogiu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (tmp - (wp.exp(v1 + 0.84) - wp.exp(v0 + 0.40)))
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.48 + v2 + 0.18) + v2) / ((v1 + 0.16 - v1 + 0.43) - 0.29))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(v1))
    v0 = (v2 - ((v1 + 0.92 - v1 + 0.89) + wp.exp(tmp + 0.81)))
    v2 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
